        "title": "feat(crabbox): add PR desktop lease workflow",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add a generic Crabbox PR desktop lease workflow for maintainer-triggered Linux and macOS inspection leases\n- install a pinned Crabbox CLI from `openclaw/crabbox` before leasing\n- post ready/status/failure handoff comments back to the target PR without exposing WebVNC credentials\n- harden lease lifecycle around stale heads, inspect failures, terminal states, duplicate creation, WebVNC bridge recovery, and PR-head race windows\n- document the first-run/default-branch proof constraint for this secret-bearing workflow\n\n## Validation\n- `node --check scripts/crabbox/pr-desktop-lease.mjs`\n- `node scripts/check-workflows.mjs`\n- `node scripts/format-docs.mjs --check`\n- `node scripts/check-docs-mdx.mjs docs/concepts/crabbox-pr-desktop-leases.md docs/concepts/mantis.md docs/docs.json`\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs test/scripts/crabbox-pr-desktop-lease.test.ts test/scripts/crabbox-pr-desktop-lease-workflow.test.ts test/scripts/test-projects.test.ts`\n- `autoreview --mode branch --base origin/main`: clean before the last two race/expiry fixes; reruns after those fixes stalled in the review engine, so the two findings were fixed manually and covered with targeted tests\n\n## Proof status\n- Not ready to undraft or merge yet unless maintainers waive the live mac proof requirement.\n- This is a generic Crabbox desktop lease workflow, not a Mantis QA workflow. No Mantis-prefixed secret fallbacks remain.\n- GitHub cannot manually dispatch a new workflow until it exists on the default branch, so first-run workflow proof still needs a trusted default-branch deployment or an operator machine.\n- Local `OPENCLAW_TESTBOX=1 pnpm check:changed` could not run because local pnpm tried to reconcile the shared worktree `node_modules`; the direct Crabbox Testbox route then failed on missing Blacksmith auth (`blacksmith auth login`).\n- Local Crabbox mac proof is blocked in this environment because AWS/Crabbox mac provider config is not available.\n",
